<style>
body
 {
  
background-color:
 red;
}
</style>

<body>
  <h1>This is a heading</h1>
  <p>This is a paragraph</p>
  <p>This is a paragraph</p>
</body>
                                                    Exercise: 3
Set the page's background color to red, by using an inline style.
<body 
style
="background-color: red">
  <h1>This is a heading</h1>
  <p>This is a paragraph</p>
  <p>This is a paragraph</p>
</body>
